' Debug-cache regression: child unique to parentB. Three distinct debug
' records, designed to push the shared DebugData table forward so the shared
' child's records, on cache hit, dedup-walk past these and land at indices
' different from the ones baked into the shared child's cached binary.
PUB run() | a, b, c
  a := 0
  b := 0
  c := 0
  debug("extraB alpha", udec_(a))
  debug("extraB beta",  udec_(b))
  debug("extraB gamma", udec_(c))
